                  "pageId": 195520,
                  "revisionId": 2696087,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Increases the drop chance of resources from normal enemy drop tables. Resources with a 100% drop chance such as a Rare Resource from a boss drop or unique resources like Steel Essence will not be increased since they already have a guaranteed drop chance to begin with."
